{
  "stem": "7873.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could have gone straight even to Hitler and asked something like that, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wasn't afraid of nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And somehow, we got him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- they canceled him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't go to Neustadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Unfortunately, you know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was him and his wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because it cost money and everything to bring him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was in Warsaw, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Warsaw was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to, somehow-- they used to have a song.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, they-- down there, they got some kind of cards, whatever, a little slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, [LAUGHS] no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle used to tell me that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we started to hear rumors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're going to send out people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to send out people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we already-- we had our foreman, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gilbert, ?] Moishe [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gilbert ?] was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a-- he spoke with the architect, the one-- he gives us the drawings for whatever we had to do, that he should say a good word, that we should go-- that we can-- would go with the first shipment.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because the-- what, what they-- even the guy said, you guys going to get [NON-ENGLISH], resettled.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never mentioned anything about any camp or anything, just resettled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they made-- every group had a captain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, the, the, the 5th of-- the 5th of November, 1942, an order came the next day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever you can carry on your-- whatever you can carry, come out in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's-- that was that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was around 10,000 the first-- the first shipment, was-- not 10,000, 1,000.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The marketplace.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything happened on the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
